<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200928/1b5f5b794129410d9a0d4874bc2bf5f0.png" /></p>
<p><strong>钦州</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200928/d39d254b58d14994a8ac1c68820791ff.png" /></p>
<p><strong>贵港</strong></p>
